Package: KidsightsPublic
Title: Kidsights Developmental Screening Scores
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Marcus", "Waldman", , "marcus.waldman@cuanschutz.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3288-4803"))
Description: Compute MAP estimates of developmental screening scores using
    Graded Response Models with fixed item parameters calibrated from Mplus.
    Supports unidimensional (Kidsights overall) and bifactor (psychosocial
    domain) scoring via CmdStan L-BFGS optimization.
